headline: 3 AI Stocks to Buy and Hold for the Rest of the Decade
summary: As 2025 approaches, investors may start to think about how they want to approach the second half of the decade.  The emergence of ChatGPT helped make Nvidia the AI stock of the decade's first half.  While it is nearly impossible to predict the best performer for the rest of the decade, investors can expect that several stocks will probably deliver strong returns.
